,"tid":1711512,"uid":91910,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"5021028fedfbe43530c08cd7b0c218019d938d73","tid":1711512,"uid":123895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"個人feel到今次勁過85嗰次<br />\n一鼓作氣 再而衰三而竭<br />\n大家繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n迫住要返既都可以一齊幫手被罷工架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"聽日係咪繼續？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:23:13.000Z","msg":"睇唔到中大咩事？dklm<br />\n聽日一定要比前兩日更大規模<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb975ecfafdd330e149598772f3ac0685ef164a7","tid":1711512,"uid":258373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"84274fb7004e698d3d98102049163d2aef8f8302","tid":1711512,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"罷佢老母"},{"pid":"39e0dc4712d46ac53579cde297b2e130abc85d8d","tid":1711512,"uid":123895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:26:54.000Z","msg":"【冷氣軍師入】 需要大幅提升塞鐵的安全度同效率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712259</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc8c98b4b1dccbe50c93f5d9a8db18e9f83e0a0d","tid":1711512,"uid":123895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39e0dc4712d46ac53579cde297b2e130abc85d8d","tid":1711512,"uid":123895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:26:54.000Z","msg":"【冷氣軍師入】 需要大幅提升塞鐵的安全度同效率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712259</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"借post<br />\n我先集合一下幾個我今日見到的方法<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n有啲人真係好賤格，用啲厚1.5-2mm（之前打錯做cm）既雙面透明膠貼痴住地鐵車門搞到山唔到閘開唔到車，細細張又睇唔到難揾到死，好黑人憎囉，啲人塞住車門都可以推翻佢出去，厚膠貼真係好拿煩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n如果唔夠人<br />\n<br />\n不如集中力量<br />\n<br />\n不斷來回：<br />\n奧運返南昌<br />\n旺角去太子<br />\n美孚返荔景<br />\n太子去九龍塘<br />\n<br />\n集中玩死一個好過分散冇效果<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n#樂富 #石硤尾 冇防暴<br />\n如有不適請參考下列指引<br />\n<br />\n教學：<br />\n1.未到站嘅時候撳緊急制。<br />\n2.覺得自己真係好暈。<br />\n3.等佢黎，用輪椅。<br />\n4.休息一陣話覺得冇事。<br />\n5.話係太焗，堅持要走。<br />\n6.唔需要白車。"},{"pid":"175d05e698e05f4245d1836ab399873a779f277b","tid":1711512,"uid":41496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9ea976f75dbaf5d9de4c9267a25ae1c8bb87d09a","tid":1711512,"uid":119897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"唔係潑冷水 香港人罷三日已經好叻 真罷 唔係被罷"},{"pid":"ad6055aa097a90d90324680355db46aa27524e7d","tid":1711512,"uid":121366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:36:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"32902f87d6e4a060c0fb854f6cf9275ddc56dda5","tid":1711512,"uid":269929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"會返工和你塞做下街坊"},{"pid":"a9d83ff085a84844679df0f2b09d4f3d5b05a291","tid":1711512,"uid":184514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"罷佢老母"},{"pid":"6636cbcc1095d81206398534e36872701a0defa7","tid":1711512,"uid":250737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:46:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b344cf4010b80651779e2432a49fa690da0a939","tid":1711512,"uid":290836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c77c5aee8134c66643ffcb98db9ba09074fb7461","tid":1711512,"uid":186640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:46:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d8ed6b7c4f8a294396b623b8769b35a1da319406","tid":1711512,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:54: